casebody.data:
Elizabeth H. Wyskiel, Administratrix (Estate of Raymond A. Hubbard) v. City Plan and Zoning Commission of Middletown Robert H. Fraser, in support of the motion. Robert H. Fraser, for the named plaintiff. Richard G. Robinson and Milton Sorokin, for the plaintiff Middlesex Development Company, Inc. No appearance for the defendant. Submitted December 15, 1972 decided January 2, 1973 Argued January 2

decided January 2, 1973

The plaintiff’s motion for leave to withdraw the appeal from the Court of Common Pleas in Middle-sex County is denied.

The plaintiff’s motion to dismiss the appeal from the Court of Common Pleas in Middlesex County is granted.
